bIsFieldOfViewSupported: Whether FieldOfView in frame data can be used
bIsAspectRatioSupported: Whether AspectRatio in frame data can be used
bIsFocalLengthSupported: Whether FocalLength in frame data can be used
bIsProjectionModeSupported: Whether ProjectionMode in frame data can be used
FilmBackWidth: Used with CinematicCamera. Values greater than 0 will be applied
FilmBackHeight: Used with CinematicCamera. Values greater than 0 will be applied
bIsApertureSupported: Whether Aperture in frame data can be used
bIsFocusDistanceSupported: Whether FocusDistance in frame data can be used
bIsDepthOfFieldSupported: Set to false to force the camera to disable depth of field
bIsLocationSupported: Whether location in frame data should be used
bIsRotationSupported: Whether rotation in frame data should be used
bIsScaleSupported: Whether scale in frame data should be used
PropertyNames: Names for each curve values that will be sent for each frame
